"]},{"title":"Mango coulis","content":["20 g coconut sugar","200 g mango, flesh only, plus extra finely sliced for garnishing","1 tbsp lemon juice"]}],"id":"r71048","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-73CMFUPJUpI\/XZan-fc0c_I\/AAAAAAAAhFw\/oBRklasCqtsSMoQeTyR4Fa2dbasj7I6AQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_admN69l9XoYLAp6d.png","title":"Mango cheesecake","publishedAt":"2014-05-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{},"usefulItems":"baking paper, springform cake tin (20 cm), oven, refrigerator","basicInfo":["medium","20m","6h 35m","12 slices"]}